node.text: A quick walk around! The Chiron PurSport has a 8.0L W16 with 1,500hp and 1,180 lb-ft. 0-60mph in 2.3 sec. 0-100 in 4.4 sec. 0-150mph in 8.6 sec. 0-200mph in 15.7 sec. 7 speed dual-clutch transmission. 4400 pounds. What do you guys think? #bugatti #chiron #chironpursport #pursport

node.text: @lamborghinibroward - The EVO RWD ( Rear Wheel Drive ) and it’s 5.2L V10 with 610hp and 413lb-ft of torque. 0-62mph in 3.3 seconds and a 202mph top speed. The RWD EVO is lighter at 3062 pounds. Check out those seats! 😍 Make sure to follow the guys at @lamborghinibroward! Tomorrow we will have a contest for you guys! Stay tuned! 😁 #LamborghiniBroward #HuracanEvoRWD
